" PROJECTS                       ┌ grove ─────────────────────────────┐"
" ────────────────────────────   │                                    │"
"▸▼ grove                        │  Select a worktree from the sidebar│"
"   ○ main                       │  (↑↓ or j/k to navigate)           │"
"   ● ┌ Help ────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │"
"   ● │                                                          │n si│"
"     │  Sidebar                                                 │    │"
" ▼ do│    j / k             move up / down                      │    │"
"   ○ │    h / l             collapse / expand repo              │    │"
"   ● │    Enter             activate worktree + focus           │    │"
"     │    w                 new worktree (branch picker)        │    │"
" ────│    W                 remove worktree                     │    │"
" [a] │    a                 add repository                      │    │"
" [w] │    R                 remove repository                   │    │"
"     │    r                 refresh git status                  │    │"
" j/k │    L                 view background warnings log        │    │"
" ?   │                                                          │    │"
" q   │  Main (terminal)                                         │    │"
"     │    Ctrl+t            new tab                             │    │"
"     │    Ctrl+w            close tab                           │    │"
"     │    Ctrl+h / Ctrl+l   previous / next tab                 │    │"
"     │    Ctrl+\            enter scrollback mode               │    │"
"     │    scroll wheel      enter scrollback + scroll           │    │"
"     │                                                          │    │"
"     │  Scrollback mode                                         │    │"
"     │    j / k / ↑↓        scroll one line                     │    │"
"     │    PageUp / PageDown  scroll 20 lines                    │    │"
"     │    g / G             top / bottom                        │    │"
"     │    i / q / Esc       exit scrollback mode                │    │"
"     │                                                          │    │"
"     │  Diff (focus=Main)                                       │    │"
"     │    Ctrl+d            toggle diff view                    │    │"
"     │    j / k             prev / next file                    │    │"
"     │    Tab               list ↔ content                      │    │"
"     │    J / K             scroll content                      │    │"
"     └ ↓ more ──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │"
"                                │                                    │"
"                                │                                    │"
"                                │                                    │"
"                                └────────────────────────────────────┘"
